dc_title_s: Metsker's road map of Pierce Co. & vicinity, Washington : the playground of the Northwest
dc_description_s: Includes indexes to towns and lakes.; Shows paved roads, main traveled highways, other roads, railroads, electric railways, trails, reserve boundaries and township and section lines.; Relief shown by hachures and spot heights.|85 x 112 centimeters|Scale approximately 1:126,720; 1/2 inch = 1 mile.|General Map Collection
